{"tid":250624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[陪葬] 戇鳩民眾踴殘橋睇女人自殺 橋斷釀3死多人失蹤","createTime":"2017-05-20T08:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T13:08:12.000Z","uid":17103,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89aae8693651def3bce40b8fe760d35c86cbb530","tid":250624,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"【八卦奪命】民眾踴殘橋睇女人自殺 橋斷釀3死多人失蹤<br />\n即時國際 <br />\n<br />\n2017-05-20 01:19:59 HKT<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170520/large/1495210918_0759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170520%2Flarge%2F1495210918_0759.jpg&h=dde6ab47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度一批民眾聚集在一條殘舊的橋上，圍觀一名女子自殺，怎料橋身不勝負荷，當場坍塌，多人掉落河中，事件據報至少3人死亡，多人失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n《印度徒報》引述果阿邦(Goa)警方說，近50名印度民眾，周四聚集在果阿邦南部祖阿里河一條歷史悠久的舊橋上，準備觀看一名女子自殺，但橋身突然倒塌，民眾紛紛墜入河中。<br />\n<br />\n警方和消防員接報後展開救援，救起5人，另有約10人自行游返岸上，到周四晚，救援人員撈到一具屍體，但仍有數十人下落不明。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示無法確定當時橋上的人數，仍繼續在河上搜救，印度海軍潛水員亦加入協助。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞《光華日報》/印度Times Now"},{"pid":"7bf4f78f36739104817e72f3284b012ac121b7f8","tid":250624,"uid":75117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:35:14.000Z","msg":"睇人仆街點知自己仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9346806cf56a010c71bf3a8ea3e850008b4834ba","tid":250624,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b26ae2dff6171ec7496537093897f0f2e90611b","tid":250624,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T08:37:59.000Z","msg":"陪葬<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1e81fc7c8639ac11019438268fc2eed2bc1856","tid":250624,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dis